  "text": "where T is the temperature and in units of \u00b0C. The validity of this correlation is in \u03c6 = 0.0625 % to 5 % and T = 25 \u00b0C to 50 \u00b0C intervals. The viscosity of ZnO-EG nanofluid can be calculated by using following correlation proposed by Esfe and Saedodin [CITATION_1] which is based on experimental data obtained for ZnO-EG nanofluid; ",
